            "title": "实验教学平台Js审计，弱口令",
            "summary": "<p>经过信息收集发现了一个实验教学平台</p>\n",
            "content_html": "<p>经过信息收集发现了一个实验教学平台</p>\n\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"569\" height=\"363\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>运气很好，用123456/123456的时候发现响应包是200（非常变态的一个系统，只要账号是123456，就会显示成功，但是会缺少字段，其他账号登录却正常，应该是测试账号），显示登录成功，但是前端响应登陆失败，于是我开始js审计<br>发现是因为响应包缺少了userrole和username字段<br>手动添加上，成功进入后台<br>继续js审计<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"528\" height=\"213\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>发现超级管理员<br>难道说他是根据userrole来判断权限的？<br>将本地存储的userrole修改为超级管理员<br>成功进入超级管理员页面<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-3-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1638\" height=\"312\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-3-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-3-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-3-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-3-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-3-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-3-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>测试功能点<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-4-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1395\" height=\"719\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-4-3-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-4-3-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-4-3-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-4-3-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-4-3-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-4-3-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1337\" height=\"759\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-6-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"923\" height=\"435\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-4-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-4-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-4-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-4-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-4-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-4-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>创建超级管理员2310250786/123456成功<br>确认拥有管理员权限，可重置任意用户账号<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1348\" height=\"326\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>共计泄露1.8w用户<br><br>测试其他用户越权<br>创建教师账号 2310250787/123456<br>创建课程负责人 2310250788/123456<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-8-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"917\" height=\"424\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-8-2-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-8-2-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-8-2-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-8-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-8-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-8-2-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>访问https://xxx.xxx.edu.cn/experiment/#/home/userInfo<br>成功访问<br>测试添加账号<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/Tu-Pian-9-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"570\" height=\"493\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-9-2-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-9-2-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-9-2-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-9-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-9-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/5/responsive/Tu-Pian-9-2-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>越权创建超级管理员账号<br><br></p>",
